Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.78,0:00:03.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since the powers of the Soul Reaper\Nwere thrust upon me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.68,0:00:05.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,my whole world has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.78,0:00:07.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Substitute Soul Reaper,\NIchigo Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.68,0:00:11.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wield this sword\Nwith all of my soul and strength
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.72,0:00:14.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to protect my precious friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.83,0:00:25.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are my one and only.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.80,0:00:31.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No one can take your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.49,0:00:36.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never fade, my only flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.62,0:00:49.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sun never blinds you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.69,0:00:55.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are like a flower that blooms in shade.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.26,0:01:05.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Exhale those feelings you hold inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.14,0:01:15.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are my one and only;\Nnow and forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.02,0:01:25.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The day may come\Nwhen all will rise against us,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.59,0:01:30.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but I will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.58,0:01:34.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never give up, my only flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.63,0:01:41.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,TIME NOTICE THAT\NYOU SHOULD NOTICE THAT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.29,0:01:45.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,NOTICE THAT THERE’S NO OTHER
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:52.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.31,0:01:53.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How are we going to get away?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.61,0:01:56.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.65,0:01:58.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, so that's it…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.07,0:02:03.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.99,0:02:06.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here’s an added bonus!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.53,0:02:19.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.88,0:02:21.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:23.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!\NRun away quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:29.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:43.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,C-Could it be--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.88,0:02:45.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.17,0:02:48.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I just realized something terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.36,0:02:50.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kon! Calm down!\NWhat's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:53.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There’s a possibility that among us…\Namong us…!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:56.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's a rain man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.34,0:03:02.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now's not the time to confuse us\Nwith superstitions!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.39,0:03:04.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the rain man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.07,0:03:07.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pay attention to that story!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.78,0:03:10.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:11.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:26.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A-Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.32,0:03:29.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sure is a nice rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:32.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The perfect conditions!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.57,0:03:36.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we told you…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.12,0:03:38.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can't run away from water…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:44.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, lackeys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:45.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:48.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you notice this earlier?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:49.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:53.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That doll is difficult to track\Nwhile it's combined with water…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.32,0:03:56.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really. What a troublesome opponent…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:03.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why you…!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.37,0:04:06.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's about time\Nwe get them…Ban?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:10.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I think so, Ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:11.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:11.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:16.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They combined!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:18.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And they’re becoming bigger…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:24.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.69,0:04:27.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue! Chad!\NTake Ishida and run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.77,0:04:29.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:49.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Zabimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:04:58.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.83,0:05:00.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it really wasn't any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:03.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sha! Red Flame Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.12,0:05:08.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did that get’em?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:11.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.28,0:05:13.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.41,0:05:18.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:20.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo! Ren--!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:24.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:33.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad! Inoue! Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:34.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:36.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:41.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough! Just leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.81,0:05:45.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you have the time to complain,\Nthen just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:48.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We can't allow everyone\Nto be caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:51.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.42,0:05:53.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.13,0:05:53.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:56.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo is all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:05:58.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's protect Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.82,0:06:21.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That seems to be\Na valuable marionette…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:29.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's just old.\NI don't think it has any value…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.23,0:06:32.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kariya is worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.29,0:06:35.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think you should return?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:39.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't follow anyone's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,0:06:44.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's an order from\Nthe man you love?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.65,0:06:49.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even love grows old…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:50.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It definitely grows old,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:54.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,especially if you think\Nyou're being controlled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:07:00.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It appears Kariya…\Nis making his move soon…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:02.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.07,0:07:06.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bounts are self-reliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:08.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just let him do what he wants…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:13.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Kariya so soft on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:16.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You seem so slow to me…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.61,0:07:20.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're much more of\Na boy than you look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.51,0:07:25.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The world doesn't move\Non just momentum.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:32.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Unnecessary ambition will destroy you…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:34.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:36.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:47.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m off for the night!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:50.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Starting tomorrow,\NI’ll be working hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.59,0:07:54.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That storeowner sure was kind\Nto let me work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.46,0:07:57.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He even let me have\Nthe remaining packed lunches.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:07:58.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Ganju…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:07:59.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.39,0:08:01.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.95,0:08:08.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis felt a strange presence\Nso she told me to investigate…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.99,0:08:12.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?\NThen that's the same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.40,0:08:15.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Unohana also ordered me…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:18.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We both have it rough, don't we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.05,0:08:18.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.65,0:08:23.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hana…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.11,0:08:24.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:28.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This Spiritual Pressure…\NCould it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.00,0:08:34.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Red Flame Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:38.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ghoul!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:39.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Günter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.09,0:08:45.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Close!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:45.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Close!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:50.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:52.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, the Quincy will get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:53.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.20,0:09:05.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:08.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? It suddenly cracked!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.46,0:09:10.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's because those twin Bounts left!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:11.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:13.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They went in Ishida's direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:15.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.21,0:09:21.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sado, where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:23.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, it's bad\Nif we're in this rain…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:25.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the usual factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.11,0:09:25.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If we go there,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.97,0:09:28.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo and the others should realize\Nand follow us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:35.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:35.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.68,0:09:36.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.36,0:09:43.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! They got ahead of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.22,0:09:46.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:09:59.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.03,0:10:01.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Santenkesshun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:03.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I reject!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.28,0:10:05.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:13.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.41,0:10:18.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, there's no escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:20.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurodo! Noba!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:22.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.17,0:10:24.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Just the two of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.14,0:10:40.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We always have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.27,0:10:43.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.75,0:10:46.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not in this rain…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:55.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.11,0:11:02.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.73,0:11:04.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It'll turn back to normal,\Nno matter how many times you try!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.72,0:11:11.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ban! We can't separate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:16.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:20.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.65,0:11:22.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:27.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sado! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.65,0:11:28.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:29.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:33.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But what happened all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.11,0:11:34.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.20,0:11:40.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Those twin brats…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:41.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:44.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They never attacked separately…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.29,0:11:45.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:47.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It feels as if…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.65,0:11:51.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,they control that doll by\Ncombining their powers…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.95,0:11:54.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They're using that\Nresonance phenomenon
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:55.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,which twins are said to have, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.68,0:11:59.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they can combine\Ntheir dolls into one…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.14,0:12:02.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Together, they're complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:04.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:44.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Koga?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:52.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.11,0:12:55.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can read. This is fine…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:57.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're the same as always, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.99,0:13:01.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dry your clothes. You'll catch a cold…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:04.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pour you some tea\Nat ten o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:07.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t trouble yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:10.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what happened\Nto everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:13.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're the first one…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:24.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A place with no water?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.01,0:13:26.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This place is leaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:27.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:29.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's better than outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:30.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sado.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.59,0:13:31.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:33.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida has a fever…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:35.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:39.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone… Just leave me here…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:41.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.86,0:13:44.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your concern, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.78,0:13:47.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be a burden\Non you any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:48.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.53,0:13:51.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's a limit to how pathetic\NI can get!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.25,0:13:58.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then come with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:00.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make you even\Nif you don't want us to…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.86,0:14:11.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:18.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We've got…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:20.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,a Quincy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:26.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.32,0:14:28.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can't use that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.48,0:14:33.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:35.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:38.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you care what happens\Nto this Quincy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:41.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.95,0:14:44.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.01,0:14:45.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:46.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.92,0:14:48.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.41,0:14:50.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:53.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Are you stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:54.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Besides…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.61,0:14:57.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you should run away quickly if\Nyou care for your lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.74,0:14:58.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:00.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We still haven't shown you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:04.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ghoul and Günter's true abilities,\Nhave we?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:09.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ghoul and Günter tell us\Nthey want to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.53,0:15:22.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.41,0:15:43.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't breathe…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.72,0:15:48.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.39,0:15:52.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.85,0:15:55.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.65,0:16:01.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We can go\Nanywhere there's water!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:05.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A human body is 70% water, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:07.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ghoul! Günter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:08.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tear their bodies…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:12.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Into pieces from the inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.55,0:16:19.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:26.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kon! Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.39,0:16:27.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say unreasonable things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:31.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:34.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:34.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:35.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.75,0:16:36.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.46,0:16:37.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Try what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:40.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It should be over soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.51,0:16:42.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If we get serious…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.20,0:16:44.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.79,0:16:46.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ho! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:50.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:51.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:52.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:57.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ban! Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:16:59.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.78,0:17:01.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?!\NWhere'd you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:03.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right, this is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:04.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.03,0:17:08.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can you take them further away? Noba!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.22,0:17:11.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is the best I can do…\NJust a little further!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:14.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:30.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:32.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You saved us, Noba…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:34.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They're one person in two…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:38.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They were controlling two dolls by\Nsharing their thoughts via resonance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:43.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Conversely, if one loses consciousness,\Nthey can't resonate…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:45.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So neither one can control their dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.57,0:17:47.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Noba?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.91,0:17:48.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:51.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ban! Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.32,0:17:55.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ban! Wake up! Please wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:56.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now's our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:12.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You've lost! Give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.49,0:18:13.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.20,0:18:18.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can do this! I can!\NI can do this by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:20.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Zeige dih Ghoul!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:27.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shakkaho! Red Flame Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:31.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do it, Ghoul!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:35.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:40.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless!\NWe don't have enough firepower!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.73,0:18:42.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shakkaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.11,0:18:50.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you aiming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.82,0:18:55.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can do this by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.08,0:18:56.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:18:58.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's around here.\NLet's go, Hana!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:18:59.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.54,0:19:00.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:01.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Seppa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.47,0:19:04.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ghoul!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:06.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.39,0:19:07.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.47,0:19:10.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! There you are.\NI thought you were here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:11.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.80,0:19:13.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! You!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:16.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Ichigo, it's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.85,0:19:17.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ganju!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.48,0:19:20.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:23.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hanataro?!\NWhy are you both here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.32,0:19:26.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.03,0:19:27.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Besides that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:30.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,did you say that you didn't\Nhave enough firepower?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:33.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Firepower is a Shiba family patent!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.21,0:19:35.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.31,0:19:36.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, Ganju!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:42.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hit an extra large one\Nagainst that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.35,0:19:47.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I want to eat that\Npacked lunch I got from the boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:51.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ghoul! What are you doing?! Go!\N1B	01:45:23:11	01:45:24:06	Number One
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:54.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.90,0:19:56.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Move, Ghoul!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:19:59.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ta…ma…ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.78,0:20:04.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! It went out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.87,0:20:06.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:24.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hot! Hot! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.01,0:20:26.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hot! Hot! Hot!\N Hot! Hot! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:20:57.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:04.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.04,0:21:06.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They've turned to dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.42,0:21:09.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they looked like children,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:12.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,they were probably past\Ntheir limits as living beings…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.28,0:21:17.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Losing their dolls may\Nhave pushed them past that point…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:21.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.65,0:21:24.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Inoue?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.85,0:21:26.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Ishida--?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.95,0:21:57.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Master Kariya, welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.90,0:22:02.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, good work as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.52,0:22:04.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.77,0:22:07.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You suck up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.60,0:22:10.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Udagawa, where are Ho and Ban?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.74,0:22:12.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that they were defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.62,0:22:14.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Their presence has disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.61,0:22:15.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.21,0:22:40.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count one! And move on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.68,0:22:43.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count two! And take a break
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.32,0:22:45.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count three! And think through
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.87,0:22:48.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll just go at my own pace
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.29,0:22:55.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Time goes by, and I get left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.73,0:22:58.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I say,\N“don’t forget that anxious feeling”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.43,0:23:00.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They tell me,\N“A reckless challenge is meaningless”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.96,0:23:03.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I say “don’t give up.”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.47,0:23:13.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,(Offense!) At times when\Nthe going gets tough, I raise my voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.60,0:23:23.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,(Offense!) And head toward\Nthe direction of my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.10,0:23:33.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing to be afraid of\Nthat towering wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.16,0:23:43.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never losing sight in this life\Nwithout answers
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.29,0:23:46.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep My Pace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.96,0:23:56.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count one! And move on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.55,0:23:59.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count two! And take a break
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.32,0:24:01.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count three! And think through
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.76,0:24:06.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll just go at my own pace
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.71,0:24:11.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida, that bastard!\NWhere did he disappear to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.23,0:24:13.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he's lost his Quincy powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.26,0:24:16.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,he still has the important job\Nof doing maintenance on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.33,0:24:17.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.46,0:24:19.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all I'm good for?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.13,0:24:19.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.94,0:24:21.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have enough clothes\Nto wear in the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.78,0:24:23.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won't go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.67,0:24:34.66,On Top,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Golden Illustrated Guide\Nto Soul Reapers after these messages!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.67,0:24:36.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.14,0:24:37.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Golden!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.09,0:24:44.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hisagi… I-It's painful…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.22,0:24:47.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kira… I may not be able\Nto go on any longer…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.73,0:24:52.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I die…\Ntake care of my subordinates…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.51,0:24:56.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No… Hisagi, get a hold of yourself…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.37,0:25:01.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Their livers are weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.29,0:25:03.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They drink too much sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.63,0:25:12.61,On Top,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tune in again!